E-commerce Website
This e-commerce site is designed to provide a seamless shopping experience, combining a clean user interface with intuitive navigation. The site features a homepage with product listings, filtering options, and detailed product pages, ensuring easy browsing and purchasing. Built using HTML, CSS, and JavaScript, the website showcases my skills in front-end development, focusing on responsive design and user-centered interactions. Highlights include a streamlined shopping cart function, a visually appealing layout, and optimized loading times for a smooth user experience.

Features:

Responsive Design: Optimized for mobile and desktop viewing to ensure accessibility across devices.
Dynamic Shopping Cart: Allows users to add, update, or remove items with instant visual feedback.
Clean Product Filtering: Enables users to find products based on categories and price ranges.
